Larry J. Merlo -- President, CEO & Director

Yeah, Bob, it's Larry. I'll start, and I think Eva will jump in, in terms of your second question. But to your point, we're really pleased with how the integration is going, the over delivery to our initial guidance is largely in two areas, one is the formulary optimization, and the second one is, we're just being able to transition functions a bit faster than we had modeled and probably the biggest example is the consolidation of our mail operations and pharmacy.

