And so the report that -- what we're doing with the portfolio this year is, it's a multi-year strategy and we are ensuring that our consumers will have choices that will better meet their specific needs. And what we're really very happy about where our preliminary benchmarks came in as Larry said, we're at 31, we qualified 31 out of 34 regions. So we feel good about where we're positioned relative to Part D next year.

Ricky Goldwasser -- Morgan Stanley -- Analyst

